            "details": "You have a stapler, a book, and a coffee mug. Describe your items."
          }
        ],
        "steps": [
          "Student 1 points to the pen and asks, 'What is this?'",
          "Student 2 responds, 'This is a stapler.'",
          "Student 1 asks about the notebook, 'What are these?'",
          "Student 2 replies, 'Those are my papers.'",
          "Student 1 points to the coffee mug and asks, 'What is that?'"
        ]
      },
